title: 'As good as I've ever seen' - where does Jacks' catch rank?
subtitle: England all-rounder Will Jacks takes a stunning catch to remove stand-in Australia captain Steve Smith on day two in Brisbane - and it gets big praise from Michael Vaughan.
full_text: England all-rounder Will Jacks takes a stunning catch to remove stand-in Australia captain Steve Smith on day two in Brisbane - and it gets big praise from Michael Vaughan.
